section.section:
Articles of dissolution shall contain:
The name of the limited liability company;
The date of filing of the articles of organization and each amendment thereto;
The date of the dissolution; and
Any other information the members determine.

Articles of continuation shall contain:
The name of the limited liability company;
The date of filing of the articles of dissolution;
The date of dissolution set forth in the articles of dissolution;
The date the members agreed to continue the limited liability company; and
Any other information the members determine.
